high_descs: Pick up the apple from the sink.
Turn around then turn left to face the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave and cook it then take it out.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Put the apple in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Cook the apple from the sink in the microwave and put it in the fridge.

high_descs: Walk forward to the sink and stop.
Pick up the apple from the sink.
Turn around, take one step and turn left to face the microwave.

Open the microwave door, put the apple inside on the left side of the black plate, turn on the microwave for a a few seconds, open the door and take out the cooked apple, then shut the microwave door.
Turn right and take four steps, turn left to face the refrigerator.
Open the fridge and place the apple on the second shelf to the left of the green goblet.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved apple into the refrigerator.

high_descs: Go forward and stand to face the sink with the apple in it.
Pick the apple up out of the sink.
Turn to the right and face the microwave.
Put the apple in and shut the door and then open the door and take the apple out and shut the door again.
Move to the right and stand to face the fridge.
Put the apple in the fridge and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple in the fridge.
